. It offers programs for all stages of education, from bachelor&#8217;s degrees to doctorates.<\/p>\n<p>With a focus on leadership, DBU integrates faith into its curriculum across various fields like business, science, and even the arts. It boasts small class sizes for more interaction with professors and even has programs to help students find internships.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2>2. University of the Cumberlands<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Main campus: Williamsburg, Kentucky<\/li>\n<li>Tuition range: $12K\/year<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ucumberlands.edu\/\">Official website<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>The University of the Cumberlands<\/strong>, a university in Williamsburg, Kentucky, is a great option for work-study programs for international students in the US. This educational institution is one of the day one CPT universities that allows you to work while you study.<\/p>\n<p>They primarily focus on liberal arts programs but also offer Bachelor&#8217;s, Master&#8217;s, and even Doctorate degrees. From Business Administration to Psychology and Physician Assistant Studies, there&#8217;s a wide range of programs to choose from.<\/p>\n<p>if you want to know about <a href=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/best-countries-to-study-abroad\/\">Best countries to study abroad<\/a> read this article:<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"PfgE7uRUjr\"><p><a href=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/best-countries-to-study-abroad\/\">The Best Countries to Study Abroad | Top Ten of 2023<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"&#8220;The Best Countries to Study Abroad | Top Ten of 2023&#8221; &#8212; Abroadin \" src=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/best-countries-to-study-abroad\/embed\/#?secret=XYen3POXwo#?secret=PfgE7uRUjr\" data-secret=\"PfgE7uRUjr\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\